PI\xae Web API

Help Page Home

ItemBase

The ItemBase class is the base class for all items in Project Insight. All items (Projects, Tasks, Folders, Files, etc) inherit from the ItemBase class. The ItemBase class contains the business logic and properties which are common to all items in the system including permissions, the item name, description, child items parent items and more. The ItemBase object handles the business logic and data access for the specialized business object, ItemBase. The class inherits from BusinessObjectBase class.

ItemBase

The ItemBase class is the base class for all items in Project Insight. All items (Projects, Tasks, Folders, Files, etc) inherit from the ItemBase class. The ItemBase class contains the business logic and properties which are common to all items in the system including permissions, the item name, description, child items parent items and more. The ItemBase object handles the business logic and data access for the specialized business object, ItemBase. The class inherits from BusinessObjectBase class.
